<subSubSection pageId="16" pageNumber="27" type="distribution">
<paragraph pageId="16" pageNumber="27">Distribution, habitat, and remarks.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="16" pageNumber="27">This is a poorly understood species that occurs in South American lowland forest. It has been recorded from French Guiana, Peru, Bolivia, and Brazil (AM, MT).</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
